OL,3,CBenefits crackdown announced by
OL,4,Cgovernment in plan to save #5bn by 2030
OL,6,FThe changes include tightening the
OL,7,Feligibility criteria for disability
OL,8,Fbenefits, scrapping a controversial
OL,9,Fbenefits assessment, and raising the
OL,10,Fbasic rate of universal credit while
OL,11,Fcutting the higher rate for those too
OL,12,Fill to work.
OL,14,F"Millions of people who could work
OL,15,F(are) trapped on benefits", Kendall
OL,16,Ftold MPs in the House of Commons on
OL,17,FTuesday, insisting the current welfare
OL,18,Fsystem is "holding the country back".
