OL,6,FKendall announced the eligibility
OL,7,Fcriteria for Pip will be tightened,
OL,8,Fwith people having to prove more
OL,9,Fsevere difficulties in order to
OL,10,Fqualify.
OL,12,FPip is a benefit designed to help
OL,13,Fpeople with a disability to pay for
OL,14,Fadditional costs, such as wheelchairs,
OL,15,Fcars, above average bills, carers, and
OL,16,Fspecialist equipment.
OL,18,FThe benefit can be claimed by people
OL,19,Fboth in and out of work and is not
OL,20,Fmeans-tested. Payments range from
OL,21,F#1,500 and #9,600 a year.
