OL,6,FKendall also announced the government
OL,7,Fis scrapping the controversial work
OL,8,Fcapability assessment (WCA) by 2028.
OL,10,FThe move will end a system where
OL,11,Fbenefits payments are linked to
OL,12,Fsomeone's capacity to work, instead
OL,13,FKendall said extra income will be
OL,14,Favailable solely through the Pip
OL,15,Fassessment.
OL,17,FThe WCA is currently used to determine
OL,18,Fwho is eligible for incapacity
OL,19,Fbenefits through Universal Credit.
