OL,6,F"Going through the WCA is complex,
OL,7,Ftime-consuming and often stressful for
OL,8,Fclaimants, especially if they also
OL,9,Fhave to go through the PIP
OL,10,Fassessment," Kendall told MPs.
OL,12,F"More fundamentally, it's based on a
OL,13,Fbinary can, can't work divide when we
OL,14,Fknow the truth is that many people's
OL,15,Fphysical and mental health conditions
OL,16,Ffluctuate."
