OL,6,FKendall announced the government will
OL,7,Fconsult on whether to merge
OL,8,Fjobseeker's allowance (JSA) and
OL,9,Femployment support allowance (ESA), a
OL,10,Fmove which would allow people who have
OL,11,Fpaid into the system to get higher
OL,12,Fbenefit payments for a period of time.
OL,14,FKendall said it was a "major reform of
OL,15,Fcontributory benefits". The proposal
OL,16,Fwould merge the two benefits into a
OL,17,Ftime-limited unemployment insurance
OL,18,Fwhich is paid at a higher rate.
