OL,6,FShadow work and pensions secretary
OL,7,FHelen Whately told the Commons: "This
OL,8,Fis a now or never chance to seize the
OL,9,Fmoment, a now or never for millions of
OL,10,Fpeople who will otherwise be signed
OL,11,Foff for what could end up being a
OL,12,Flifetime on benefits, but this
OL,13,Fannouncement today leaves me with more
OL,14,Fquestions than answers."
OL,16,FTom Waters, an Associate Director at
OL,17,Fthe Institute for Fiscal Studies said:
OL,18,F"This package is a fundamental break
OL,19,Ffrom the past few decades of welfare
OL,20,Fpolicy.
